==Text==
To Gray Mystery:

<div align="center">Hey! This should be the last phantom thief letter I'll ever send you!<br />
"When you receive a phantom thief letter, be prepared to lose something."<br />
You're ready for that, aren't you?

But don't worry!<br />
No need to guard your pockets or frantically check your bags. I'm not here to steal.<br />
I'm here for our final "split of the spoils."

This lucky cat coin has been by my side during every heist.<br />
No matter what tight spot I'm in, just holding it turns my luck from woe to weal.<br />
Regardless of what weighs on my mind, tossing it up and catching it makes my steps mysteriously lighter.

I've long seen that you also keep quite a bit of "Trickery" in your heart.<br />
Otherwise, how could you have deceived destiny and stolen from the future?<br />
So, I'll entrust this "stolen article" to you.<br />
May it help you dodge every misfortune and obtain everything you desire.


Sincerely, Kitty Phantom Thief</div>

